{"id":"5c3c04e0be23a10017086e54","title":"phantomjs on ubuntu で日本語が文字化けする件 - dev.jgs.me","image":null,"created":1402498800,"updated":1591901174,"lines":[{"id":"5c3c04e04ade4d0000c9db8c","text":"phantomjs on ubuntu で日本語が文字化けする件 - dev.jgs.me","created":1402498800,"updated":1402498800},{"id":"5c3c04e04ade4d0000c9db8d","text":"","created":1402498800,"updated":1402498800},{"id":"5c3c04e04ade4d0000c9db8e","text":"[**** TL;DR]","created":1402498800,"updated":1402498800},{"id":"5c3c04e04ade4d0000c9db8f","text":"","created":1402498800,"updated":1402498800},{"id":"5c3c04e04ade4d0000c9db90","text":" [日本語フォント]いれろ","created":1402498800,"updated":1549207223},{"id":"5c3c04e04ade4d0000c9db91","text":" [locale] を `en_US.UTF-8` にしろ","created":1402498800,"updated":1549207225},{"id":"5c3c04e04ade4d0000c9db92","text":"","created":1402498800,"updated":1402498800},{"id":"5c3c04e04ade4d0000c9db93","text":"","created":1402498800,"updated":1402498800},{"id":"5c3c04e04ade4d0000c9db94","text":"[**** 詳細]","created":1402498800,"updated":1402498800},{"id":"5c3c04e04ade4d0000c9db95","text":"","created":1402498800,"updated":1402498800},{"id":"5c3c04e04ade4d0000c9db96","text":"表題の通りで、まず [ubuntu] の locale を変更してみる。","created":1402498800,"updated":1549207229},{"id":"5c3c04e04ade4d0000c9db97","text":"","created":1402498800,"updated":1402498800},{"id":"5c3c04e04ade4d0000c9db98","text":"code:_","created":1402498800,"updated":1402498800},{"id":"5c3c04e04ade4d0000c9db99","text":" % sudo apt-get install -y language-surrpot-ja","created":1402498800,"updated":1402498800},{"id":"5c3c04e04ade4d0000c9db9a","text":" % update-locale LANG=ja_JP.UTF8","created":1402498800,"updated":1402498800},{"id":"5c3c04e04ade4d0000c9db9b","text":" % sudo vim /etc/default/locale","created":1402498800,"updated":1402498800},{"id":"5c3c04e04ade4d0000c9db9c","text":" # LANG=ja_JP.UTF-8","created":1402498800,"updated":1402498800},{"id":"5c3c04e04ade4d0000c9db9d","text":"","created":1402498800,"updated":1402498800},{"id":"5c3c04e04ade4d0000c9db9e","text":"これで[ログイン]しなおすと","created":1402498800,"updated":1549207234},{"id":"5c3c04e04ade4d0000c9db9f","text":"","created":1402498800,"updated":1402498800},{"id":"5c3c04e04ade4d0000c9dba0","text":"code:_","created":1402498800,"updated":1402498800},{"id":"5c3c04e04ade4d0000c9dba1","text":" % echo $LANG","created":1402498800,"updated":1402498800},{"id":"5c3c04e04ade4d0000c9dba2","text":" # => ja_JP.UTF-8","created":1402498800,"updated":1402498800},{"id":"5c3c04e04ade4d0000c9dba3","text":"","created":1402498800,"updated":1402498800},{"id":"5c3c04e04ade4d0000c9dba4","text":"で、[スクリーンショット]を撮ってみるも相変わらず文字化け。そうか、フォントがないのか、と気付いてフォントをインストール。","created":1402498800,"updated":1549207238},{"id":"5c3c04e04ade4d0000c9dba5","text":"","created":1402498800,"updated":1402498800},{"id":"5c3c04e04ade4d0000c9dba6","text":"code:_","created":1402498800,"updated":1402498800},{"id":"5c3c04e04ade4d0000c9dba7","text":" % wget http://ipafont.ipa.go.jp/ipafont/IPAfont00303.php","created":1402498800,"updated":1402498800},{"id":"5c3c04e04ade4d0000c9dba8","text":" % unzip IPAfont00303.php","created":1402498800,"updated":1402498800},{"id":"5c3c04e04ade4d0000c9dba9","text":" % cd IPAfont00303/","created":1402498800,"updated":1402498800},{"id":"5c3c04e04ade4d0000c9dbaa","text":" % mkdir -p /usr/share/fonts/ipa","created":1402498800,"updated":1402498800},{"id":"5c3c04e04ade4d0000c9dbab","text":" % cp *.ttf /usr/share/fonts/ipa","created":1402498800,"updated":1402498800},{"id":"5c3c04e04ade4d0000c9dbac","text":" % fc-cache -fv","created":1402498800,"updated":1402498800},{"id":"5c3c04e04ade4d0000c9dbad","text":"","created":1402498800,"updated":1402498800},{"id":"5c3c04e04ade4d0000c9dbae","text":"これでもダメ。が、調べてみると locale が `ja_JP.UTF-8` だと日本語フォントが出ないらしい。なんじゃそら。","created":1402498800,"updated":1402498800},{"id":"5c3c04e04ade4d0000c9dbaf","text":"","created":1402498800,"updated":1402498800},{"id":"5c3c04e04ade4d0000c9dbb0","text":"code:_","created":1402498800,"updated":1402498800},{"id":"5c3c04e04ade4d0000c9dbb1","text":" % sudo vim /etc/default/locale","created":1402498800,"updated":1402498800},{"id":"5c3c04e04ade4d0000c9dbb2","text":" # LANG=en_US.UTF-8","created":1402498800,"updated":1402498800},{"id":"5c3c04e04ade4d0000c9dbb3","text":"","created":1402498800,"updated":1402498800},{"id":"5c3c04e04ade4d0000c9dbb4","text":"できましたー。ちょっと [phantomjs] 殴りたい。","created":1402498800,"updated":1549207248},{"id":"5c3c04e04ade4d0000c9dbb5","text":"","created":1402498800,"updated":1402498800},{"id":"5c3c04e04ade4d0000c9dbb6","text":"[* original: http://dev.jgs.me/2014/06/12/phantomjs-on-ubuntu-japan-text-language]","created":1402498800,"updated":1402498800},{"id":"5c3c04e04ade4d0000c9dbb7","text":"#20140612 #0612","created":1402498800,"updated":1591901174},{"id":"5c5706d34ade4d000094330c","text":"","created":1549207251,"updated":1549207251}]}